It used to be their 2nd Sebastopol march. The first one, last Saturday in the rain, marked the start of Occupation Sebastopol in unity with a nearly two-month-old demonstration in New Yorks Wall Street vicinity protesting the awareness of political and financial energy in the fingers of corporations and the countries wealthiest one percent.
